### rest.nvim demo — open in Neovim, place cursor on a request, press <leader>rr.
### Re-run the last request with <leader>rl. Navigate response panes with H / L.

### GET — simple
GET https://httpbin.org/get
Accept: application/json

### GET — with query params
GET https://httpbin.org/get?foo=bar&baz=qux
Accept: application/json

### POST — JSON body
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "test",
  "value": 42
}

### Custom headers
GET https://httpbin.org/headers
X-Request-Id: demo-1234
User-Agent: rest.nvim-demo

### Variable from .env (drop a file matching .env.* next to this one)
### BASE_URL=https://httpbin.org
# GET {{BASE_URL}}/uuid
